pageProduct.name: Vitalstrength Intra-Workout stack 360g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Vital Strength’s Amino Betadex is our professional strength intra-workout super stack. Specially formulated with Beta-alanine to improve training performance and endurance with an extra buzz. Experience mental stamina & clarity and delayed fatigue- work harder for longer.

Added BCAAs ensure muscle growth & repair to support post workout gains. All this with zero added stimulants makes a revolutionary intra-workout stack loaded with natural energizers.
• Maximize endurance, performance, stamina & growth
• 1.6g Beta-alanine per serve.
• 200mg of electrolytes support hydration.
• 3.8g BCAA’s to enhance muscular growth.
• 60mg Taurine improves cognitive function and athletic performance.
• Packed with nutrients your body requires during training sessions.
• Low carb- 0.13g per serve.

Warnings

This product should be used in conjunction with an appropriate physical training or exercise program. This product is not intended as a sole source of nutrition and should be consumed in conjunction with a nutritious diet and appropriate fluid intake. Not suitable for children under 15 years or pregnant women: should be used under medical or dietetic supervision.This product contains Beta Alanine which in some people may cause a tingling effect on the skin shortly after consumption.

Common Uses

Take Amino Betadex during workouts to improve performance, delay fatigue & stimulate muscle growth

Ingredients

Citric acid, Anti-caking agent (551), Flavour, Colour (110), Sucralose (995). Made in Australia from local and imported ingredients. Allergen advice: Processed on equipment that also processes milk, egg and soy. May contain traces of gluten, dairy and other animal by-products.

Directions

Mix 5g (approx. 1/2 scoop) into 250-300ml of cold water and stir until dissolved. Best consumed during your workout. *Serving size may be increased for athletes after consultation with a fitness or health care professional.
